                        <h1 class="SWWW_H1 SWWW_MaxWidth1200">Webdesign til Mayari Animal Rescue i Cebu City</h1>
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="/Images/Case-Studies/Mayari-Rescue/Mayari-Rescue-Cebu-City-Web-Design-Sustainable-WWW-Desktop-Mobile.webp" type="image/webp" media="(max-width: 600px)" />
